    "description": "Turn-based combat stripped to the core. Get loot, optimize your equipment, defeat mighty foes, enjoy the story.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1858120/extras/0ce0e63bf0b3733132bb5e9080729506.poster.avif?t=1769005326\" width=640 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1858120/extras/0ce0e63bf0b3733132bb5e9080729506.webm?t=1769005326\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1858120/extras/0ce0e63bf0b3733132bb5e9080729506.mp4?t=1769005326\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>An idle RPG where your loot matters. Optimize your equipment, defeat mighty foes, perform dark rituals and enjoy a medieval tale of revenge in a twisted version of Brazil. Elite enemies challenge how optimized your build is while random-free combat ensures attacks never miss.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>The 3 cores of an RPG without the annoyances</li></ul>Defeat foes, get better loot, read the cutscenes. Exploration, crafting, learning various skills can all be done while fighting. <br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Deadly combat awaits</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Randomized loot slightly inspired by ARPG classics like Diablo / Path of Exile / Godsbane</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>A gripping story set in an alternative universe version of Brazil</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Help villagers, embed flowers with magic, perform rituals for the Lunar Gods. Systems inspired by the Arcanum, The Theory of Magic</li></ul><br><br><br>",
